      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That sounds really scary, I didn't realize it was that bad. I just thought since they are both just for sleep it would be fine to use them together to get some rest. But if they're so dangerous, what's a better way to do it? Like, if I take the melatonin a few hours before the zolpidem, does that make it safer so they aren't hitting me at the exact same time?",
