      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You are absolutely right to be concerned, and mixing these two medications is a fatal error that could kill you. Taking them apart doesn't make it safe; the interaction is so potent that your body will simply crash into a coma regardless of the timing. There is no \"safe\" way to combine them, and your doctor has already warned you against it. Please stop taking both and go back to your doctor immediately to find a proper, safe treatment plan for your insomnia.",
